INUMBER 1914
NAME 107
ARMOR
WORN_HEAD
PARAMETER1 10
WEIGHT 5
VOLUME 3
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Made from a strange material that looks like a silvery metal, yet is not,
the helm is free of any scratches or dents. The helm slopes up from either
side to meet at the top and flare up a bit. A visor, with eyeslits and
breathing holes swings out, and in, from the right side. Nearly indescernible
across the entire breadth of the helm are tiny lines of gold that form
intricate patterns as they swirl together.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE tokronos
VARIABLE tokronos1
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  IFITEM -1 WORN
    CLEARVERB
    ADD tokronos 1
    IFVAR tokronos < 11
      ECHO PLAYER You hear a slight buzzing sound and then a shimmering field flows from the helm to cover your entire body.
      ECHO OTHERS One of the intricate designs on the helmet glows and pulses for a moment, then a shimmering field covers %N.
      SPELL 105 20
    ENDIF
    IFVAR tokronos => 11
      ECHO PLAYER You sense that the helmet is recharging.
      ECHO OTHERS %N rubs %h helmet.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TAP -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFITEM -1 WORN
    ADD tokronos 1
    IFVAR tokronos = 1
      ECHO PLAYER You feel a slight tickling sensation at the back of your mind, as if someone, or something, was trying to make contact...
      ECHO OTHERS %N fidgets nervously and scans the area.
    ENDIF
    IFVAR tokronos = 2
      ECHO PLAYER The tickling sensation grows stronger and you faintly hear a buzzing sound interspersed with the words, "We are...zzzzzz....through.....zzzzzz....temporal....zzzzz...connection imminent."
      ECHO OTHERS %N shakes %h head as if trying to clear it of something...
    ENDIF
    IFVAR tokronos = 3
      ECHO PLAYER A clear voice begins to speak in your mind, yet you sense that the voice is coming from far away, "Contact has been established with target. Greetings, I speak to you from the year 2674. We are the creators of the device which you now wear, the KRONOS helmet. Know that it is a powerful sensing device that detects the emanations left by the passage of time.\
In many instances the emanations are strong enough for the helmet to act upon, to transport the viewer back to the time to observe history. The places where such emanations are strongest are usually the places where something historically significant has ocurred. Use this power well..you hold the only prototype of this device."
      ECHO OTHERS One of the intricate golden designs upon %N's helmet glows strongly as %N's eyes roll back and %h body becomes rigid.
      EQUAL tokronos 0
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR RNUM = 3940
    DISBAND
    ECHO PLAYER You feel a slight shifting sensation, then, in the blink of an eye, you are somewhere different...
    ECHO OTHERS %N's helmet glows strongly, each of the golden lines emanating a gleaming golden hue...the brilliance makes you blink and when you finally look up, you catch a glimpse of %N disappearing through a gap in space...
    MOVE 2695
  ENDIF
  IFVAR RNUM = 293
    DISBAND
    ECHO PLAYER You feel a slight shifting sensation, then, in the blink of an eye, you are somewhere different...
    ECHO OTHERS %N's helmet glows strongly, each of the golden lines emanating a gleaming golden hue...the brilliance makes you blink and when you finally look up, you catch a glimpse of %N disappearing through a gap in space...
    MOVE 2696
  ENDIF
  IFVAR RNUM = 201
     DISBAND
     ECHO PLAYER You feel a slight shifting sensation, then, in the blink of an eye, you are somewhere different...
     ECHO OTHERS %N's helmet glows strongly, each of the golden lines emanating a gleaming golden hue...the brilliance makes you blink and when you finally look up, you catch a glimpse of %N disappearing through a gap in space...
     MOVE 2697
  ENDIF
ENDIF
